OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLost lives of Greenland's  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FInuit children uprooted by 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FDenmark                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Six people who were part of a failed   
OL,6, 1950s social experiment have won       
OL,7, compensation from Denmark's government 
OL,8, and are expected to receive a          
OL,9, face-to-face apology from the prime    
OL,10, minister.                              
OL,12,FThey were among 22 Inuit children sent 
OL,13,Fto Denmark from Greenland in 1951 to   
OL,14,Flearn Danish. It was part of a scheme  
OL,15,Fto raise "model" Greenlanders to help  
OL,16,Fbridge Danish and indigenous cultures. 
OL,18,FHowever, the children remained         
OL,19,Fseparated from their families, lost    
OL,20,Ftheir mother tongue and struggled with 
OL,21,Fidentity issues.                       
